ninja.ugly.prevail.event.dispatcher
Interface EventDispatcher

All Known Implementing Classes:
CompositeEventDispatcher, EventBusEventDispatcher, EventDispatcher.EmptyEventDispatcher, ExecutorEventDispatcher
public interface EventDispatcher

An EventDispatcher is responsible for delivering events generated by EventFactories during operations on Chunks.

This interface is intended to be implemented by instances that use, for example, Guava's EventBus or GreenRobot's EventBus on Android. Such implementations use runtime types to match events to subscribers. As such, the methods in this class are type-free.
